trans-unit.source: Specifies a type to be passed to the <see cref="M:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.Write``1(System.String,System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSourceOptions,``0)" /> method.
trans-unit.target: Especifica um tipo a ser passado para o método <see cref="M:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.Write``1(System.String,System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSourceOptions,``0)" />.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.Write%2A> requires T to be an anonymous type or marked with the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventDataAttribute> attribute.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.Write%2A> requer T ser um tipo anônimo ou marcado com o <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventDataAttribute> atributo.

trans-unit.source: In addition, the properties of `T` must be a supported property type; either a simple framework type such as <xref:System.Int16>, <xref:System.Int32>, <xref:System.Int64>, <xref:System.String>, <xref:System.Guid>, <xref:System.DateTime> or <xref:System.DateTimeOffset>, or an array of primitive types.
trans-unit.target: Além disso, as propriedades de `T` deve ser um tipo de propriedade com suporte; uma estrutura simples, como tipo <xref:System.Int16>, <xref:System.Int32>, <xref:System.Int64>, <xref:System.String>, <xref:System.Guid>, <xref:System.DateTime> ou <xref:System.DateTimeOffset>, ou uma matriz de tipos primitivos.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventDataAttribute" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventDataAttribute" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or set the name to apply to an event if the event type or property is not explicitly named.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o nome a ser aplicado a um evento se o tipo de evento ou propriedade não for nomeado explicitamente.

trans-unit.source: The name to apply to the event or property.
trans-unit.target: O nome a ser aplicado ao evento ou propriedade.

trans-unit.source: If you call <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.Write%2A>, passing `null` for `eventName`, the event name is automatically derived from <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventDataAttribute.Name%2A> or determined based on the name of type `T`.
trans-unit.target: Se você chamar <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.Write%2A>, passando `null` para `eventName`, deriva automaticamente o nome do evento <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventDataAttribute.Name%2A> ou determinado com base no nome do tipo `T`.
